summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting overhead underground distribution easements over portions of Section 30, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Lot 21, Lake Burien Waterfront Tracts; Vacated Tract 1 of Spring Hill Vills Tracts; Lot 2, of King County Short Plat \#5850-85; Block 6, Hawima heights; Vacated 36th Avenue South; Tract 3 Block 13, of Lake Forest Park; Lot 1, King County Short Plat No. 1077038; Lot 11, Block 5, Roubins Spring Brook Addition to Riverton; and Lot 20, block 3, Stimson Park Division No. 1, and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
